WARNING: DO NOT USE THIS PROGRAM ! IT WILL DESTROY YOUR COMPUTER !

Instructions:

 $> tar xfJ ddb-VERSION.tar.xz
 $> cd ddb-VERSION
 $> ./configure
 $> make
 $> sudo make install

To format all the partitions on your first disk start the program:

 $> ddb

In order to delete all partitions from your first disk start with argument:

 $> ddb --init
